code: @Override public void collect(StreamRecord<T> record) {     try {         ClassLoader cl = record.getClass().getClassLoader().         T copied = InstantiationUtil.deserializeObject(InstantiationUtil.serializeObject(record.getValue()), cl).         outputs.add(copied).     } catch (IOException | ClassNotFoundException ex) {         throw new RuntimeException("Unable to deserialize record: " + record, ex).     } }
